===Transitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|construct||}}

#To [[build]] or [[form]] (something) by [[assemble|assembling]] [[part]]s.
#:''We '''constructed''' the radio from spares.''
#Similarly, to build (a [[sentence]] or an [[argument]]) by arranging [[word]]s or [[idea]]s.
#:''A sentence may be '''constructed''' with a subject, verb and object.''
#{{geometry}} To [[draw]] (a [[geometric]] [[figure]]) by following [[precise]] [[specification]]s and using geometric tools and techniques.
#:'''''Construct''' a circle that touches each vertex of the given triangle.''

